items.name: oGraph
items.description: oGraph is an open-source identity layer designed to solve one of the most persistent challenges in the digital ecosystem: identity fragmentation. It assigns and maintains a single, immutable ID for each verified person or company, using a combination of private and public data sources to create a comprehensive identity graph.
